</style>

<div class="dcf-header">
  <div class="dcf-header-content">
    <div class="dcf-tag">Compiled by Gemini 3.1</div>
    <h1>Howmet Aerospace (HWM)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="dcf-subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Howmet Aerospace.</p>
    <p class="dcf-date">Using latest available financials</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="dcf-container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
  <div class="dcf-verdict-card">
    <div class="dcf-verdict-label">Estimated Intrinsic Value Per Share</div>
    <div class="dcf-verdict-price">${roundedIV.toFixed(2)}</div>
    <div class="dcf-verdict-vs">vs. market price of ${priceLatest !== null ? priceLatest.toFixed(2) : 'N/A'} ({marginOfSafety !== 'N/A' ? `${marginOfSafety}%` : ''})</div>
    <div class="dcf-verdict-badge" style={`background: ${verdictColor}22; color: ${verdictColor}; border: 1px solid ${verdictColor}44;`}>
      {verdictText}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ KEY METRICS ═══ -->
  <div class="dcf-stats-row">
    <div class="dcf-stat-card">
      <div class="dcf-stat-value">${revenueHistory[0] !== null ? (revenueHistory[0]).toFixed(0) : 'N/A'}M</div>
      <div class="dcf-stat-label">Revenue (Latest)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dcf-stat-card">
      <div class="dcf-stat-value">${fcfBase !== null ? fcfBase.toFixed(0) : 'N/A'}M</div>
      <div class="dcf-stat-label">Free Cash Flow</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dcf-stat-card">
      <div class="dcf-stat-value">${epsHistory[0] !== null ? epsHistory[0].toFixed(2) : 'N/A'}</div>
      <div class="dcf-stat-label">EPS (Diluted)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dcf-stat-card">
      <div class="dcf-stat-value">{histMargin[0]?.operating !== null ? histMargin[0].operating : 'N/A'}%</div>
      <div class="dcf-stat-label">Operating Margin</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dcf-stat-card">
      <div class="dcf-stat-value">${(netCash / 1000).toFixed(1)}B</div>
      <div class="dcf-stat-label">Net Cash</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ METHODOLOGY ═══ -->
  <h2>Methodology: Two-Stage DCF</h2>
  <p>We use a <strong>two-stage discounted cash flow (DCF)</strong> model to find the intrinsic value of Howmet Aerospace.</p>

  <div class="dcf-method-step">
    <div class="dcf-step-num">1</div>
    <div class="dcf-step-content">
      <h4>Start with actual Free Cash Flow</h4>
      <p>HWM generated <strong>${fcfBase !== null ? fcfBase.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'} million</strong> in free cash flow recently.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dcf-method-step">
    <div class="dcf-step-num">2</div>
    <div class="dcf-step-content">
      <h4>Project FCF growth for 5 years (Phase 1)</h4>
      <p>We derive a <strong>{(growthRatePhase1 * 100).toFixed(1)}%</strong> annual growth rate mathematically based on recent FCF CAGR history.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dcf-method-step">
    <div class="dcf-step-num">3</div>
    <div class="dcf-step-content">
      <h4>Calculate terminal value (Phase 2)</h4>
      <p>After Year 5, we assume FCF grows at <strong>{(growthRateTerminal * 100).toFixed(1)}% forever</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dcf-method-step">
    <div class="dcf-step-num">4</div>
    <div class="dcf-step-content">
      <h4>Discount everything to present value</h4>
      <p>Future cash flows are discounted at <strong>{(discountRate * 100).toFixed(1)}%</strong>, derived directly using the 10Y Treasury (4.18%) and an equity risk premium.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dcf-method-step">
    <div class="dcf-step-num">5</div>
    <div class="dcf-step-content">
      <h4>Add net cash, divide by shares</h4>
      <p>Enterprise Value + Net Cash = Equity Value. Divide by shares outstanding ({sharesOutstanding}M) for per-share intrinsic value.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ THE THREE ASSUMPTIONS ═══ -->
  <h2>The Three Assumptions That Drive Everything</h2>

  <div class="dcf-assumption-grid">
    <div class="dcf-assumption-card">
      <div class="dcf-label">FCF Growth Rate (Years 1-5)</div>
      <div class="dcf-value">{(growthRatePhase1 * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="dcf-rationale">
        Mathematically derived by analyzing historical FCF data. We use a 3-year CAGR logic bound between 5% and 15% to remain conservative.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dcf-assumption-card">
      <div class="dcf-label">Discount Rate (WACC)</div>
      <div class="dcf-value">{(discountRate * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="dcf-rationale">
        10Y Treasury: { (riskFreeRate * 100).toFixed(2) }%. Assuming standard Equity Risk Premium of 5% and an Aerospace Beta of ~1.25. WACC derived mathematically.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dcf-assumption-card">
      <div class="dcf-label">Terminal Growth Rate</div>
      <div class="dcf-value">{(growthRateTerminal * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="dcf-rationale">
        Long-term nominal GDP proxy.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ FCF PROJECTIONS TABLE ═══ -->
  <h2>Projected Free Cash Flows</h2>
  <div class="dcf-table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Year</th>
          <th>FCF ($M)</th>
          <th>PV Factor</th>
          <th>Present Value ($M)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Base</td>
          <td>${fcfBase !== null ? fcfBase.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}</td>
          <td>—</td>
          <td>—</td>
        </tr>
        {projectedFCF.map(p => (
          <tr>
            <td>Year {p.year}</td>
            <td>${p.fcf.toLocaleString()}</td>
            <td>{p.pvFactor.toFixed(4)}</td>
            <td>${p.pvFCF.toLocaleString()}</td>
          </tr>
        ))}
        <tr class="dcf-row-total">
          <td colspan="3">Sum of Phase 1 PV</td>
          <td class="dcf-highlight-cell">${pvPhase1.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ TERMINAL VALUE ═══ -->
  <h3>Terminal Value</h3>
  <div class="dcf-table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Component</th>
          <th>Value ($M)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Year 6 FCF</td>
          <td>${Math.round(fcfYear6).toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Terminal Value</td>
          <td>${terminalValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="dcf-row-total">
          <td>PV of Terminal Value</td>
          <td class="dcf-highlight-cell">${pvTerminalValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ FINAL CALCULATION ═══ -->
  <h3>Final Valuation</h3>
  <div class="dcf-table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Component</th>
          <th>Value ($M)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>PV of Phase 1 Cash Flows</td>
          <td>${pvPhase1.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>PV of Terminal Value</td>
          <td>${pvTerminalValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>= Enterprise Value</td>
          <td>${enterpriseValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>+ Net Cash (Cash − Debt)</td>
          <td>${netCash.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>= Equity Value</td>
          <td>${equityValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>÷ Shares Outstanding</td>
          <td>{sharesOutstanding !== null ? sharesOutstanding.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="dcf-row-total">
          <td>Intrinsic Value Per Share</td>
          <td class="dcf-highlight-cell">${roundedIV.toFixed(2)}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ HISTORICAL CHARTS ═══ -->
  <h2>Financial Track Record</h2>

  <h3>Revenue ($M)</h3>
  <div class="dcf-bar-chart">
    {histRev.slice().reverse().map(r => (
      <div class="dcf-bar-row">
        <div class="dcf-bar-label">{r.year}</div>
        <div class="dcf-bar-track">
          <div class="dcf-bar-fill dcf-revenue" style={`width: ${r.value !== null ? (r.value / (Math.max(...revenueHistory.filter(v=>v!==null)) || 1)) * 100 : 0}%`}>
            ${r.value !== null ? r.value.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h3>Free Cash Flow ($M)</h3>
  <div class="dcf-bar-chart">
    {histFCF.slice().reverse().map(r => (
      <div class="dcf-bar-row">
        <div class="dcf-bar-label">{r.year}</div>
        <div class="dcf-bar-track">
          <div class="dcf-bar-fill dcf-fcf" style={`width: ${r.value !== null ? (Math.abs(r.value) / (Math.max(...fcfHistoryRaw.map(v=>Math.abs(v||0))) || 1)) * 100 : 0}%`}>
            ${r.value !== null ? r.value.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h3>Earnings Per Share (Diluted)</h3>
  <div class="dcf-bar-chart">
    {histEPS.slice().reverse().map(r => (
      <div class="dcf-bar-row">
        <div class="dcf-bar-label">{r.year}</div>
        <div class="dcf-bar-track">
          <div class="dcf-bar-fill dcf-eps" style={`width: ${r.value !== null ? (Math.abs(r.value) / (Math.max(...epsHistory.map(v=>Math.abs(v||0))) || 1)) * 100 : 0}%`}>
            ${r.value !== null ? r.value.toFixed(2) : 'N/A'}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ SENSITIVITY ANALYSIS ═══ -->
  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>

  <div class="dcf-table-wrap">
    <table class="dcf-sensitivity-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Discount Rate ↓ / Growth →</th>
          {sensitivityGrowth.map(g => (
            <th class={Math.abs(g - growthRatePhase1) < 0.001 ? 'dcf-current' : ''}>{(g * 100).toFixed(1)}%</th>
          ))}
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {sensitivityTable.map(row => (
          <tr>
            <td>{(row.dr * 100).toFixed(1)}%</td>
            {row.values.map((v, i) => (
              <td class={Math.abs(row.dr - discountRate) < 0.001 && Math.abs(sensitivityGrowth[i] - growthRatePhase1) < 0.001 ? 'dcf-current' : ''}>
                ${v}
              </td>
            ))}
          </tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ WHAT THE MODEL DOESN'T CAPTURE ═══ -->
  <h2>What This Model Doesn't Capture</h2>
